text: Mátyás Magos (born 14 March 1992) is a Hungarian football (midfielder) player who currently plays for Balassagyarmati VSE. ==Club career== He became a first squad member at Újpest FC in 2011. ==External links== * *hlsz.hu Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Footballers from Budapest Category:Hungarian footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:Balassagyarmati SE footballers Category:Újpest FC players Category:Szolnoki MÁV FC footballers Category:Vác FC players Category:Nemzeti Bajnokság I players
